        // Portfolio Section
        h2 Our Events
        .row
            .col-lg-4.col-sm-6.portfolio-item
                .card.h-100
                    a(href='#')
                        img.card-img-top(src='/img/picnic.png', alt='')
                    .card-body
                        h4.card-title
                            a(href='#') Profession Development Workshop
                        p.card-text
                            | We are proud to announce that we have an ongoing workshop with a representative that works at Microsoft! From learning what is happening in the industry right now to finding a job. This is the place to be!
            .col-lg-4.col-sm-6.portfolio-item
                .card.h-100
                    a(href='#')
                        img.card-img-top(src='/img/icpc.png', alt='')
                    .card-body
                        h4.card-title
                            a(href='#') ICPC 
                        p.card-text
                            | Each fall we compete in ICPC or the International Collegiate Programming Contest. This is a great place to get recognized by companies, compete with other schools, and show off what you can do!
            .col-lg-4.col-sm-6.portfolio-item
                .card.h-100
                    a(href='#')
                        img.card-img-top(src='/img/hackathon.png', alt='')
                    .card-body
                        h4.card-title
                            a(href='#') Azalea Hackathon
                        p.card-text
                            | In the Spring Azalea Health hosts thier annual hackathon. It is a programming competition where you and other students can collaboratively develop innovative ideas, software applications, and show off your skills. Did we mention cash prizes?
            .col-lg-4.col-sm-6.portfolio-item
                .card.h-100
                    a(href='#')
                        img.card-img-top(src='/img/picnicCurrent.png', alt='')
                    .card-body
                        h4.card-title
                            a(href='#') Annual Picnic
                        p.card-text
                            | Mid spring each year we host an annual picnic where professors and students alike get together and mingle. We grill some food, play sports, and take the time to meet other people in the department we might not cross paths with. 
            .col-lg-4.col-sm-6.portfolio-item
                .card.h-100
                    a(href='#')
                        img.card-img-top(src='/img/game.png', alt='')
                    .card-body
                        h4.card-title
                            a(href='#') Game Night
                        p.card-text
                            | Enjoy gaming? So do we! Each semester we host a game night were we get together and have fun. We generally have pizza, board games, card games, and consoles. All in an effort to blow off some steam after a long semester!
            .col-lg-4.col-sm-6.portfolio-item
                .card.h-100
                    a(href='#')
                        img.card-img-top(src='/img/guestph.png', alt='')
                    .card-body
                        h4.card-title
                            a(href='#') Guest Speakers
                        p.card-text
                            | Throughout the semester we will have guest speakers. Most are Alumni or their colleagues. If you didn't know we have Alumni from Amazon, Microsoft, and Google! You never know who will show up.
