                    li Github
                    li New Languages
                    li Programming Concepts
                    li Resumes and Mock Interviews
                    li Current Events
                p
                    | This is a highlighted list and other topics are also covered. There is so much going on that not everything can be listed here. We also run a survey at the beginning of each semester to determine what are the best topics to cover. We try to be as flexible as possible.
